    1.  If you are compiling a kernel-mode miniport driver, define:
            #define NDIS_MINIPORT_DRIVER 1
            #define NDIS630_MINIPORT 1
        Additionally, if you are compiling a WDM or WDF (i.e., KMDF) driver,
